<h1>MacBook Repair Options Guide</h1>

<p class="lead">When your Mac needs repair, you have choices. Apple, independent repair shops, DIY, or replacement. Each option has trade-offs, and what makes sense depends on your situation. This guide provides neutral information to help you make an informed decision.</p>

